{"type": "article", "id": 11600, "title": "可站立的剪刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-03T11:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001738YnN7qochOGBf2u5J.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Alessio Romano 设计的这款剪刀灵感来自平常使用电脑时的 “剪切” 快捷键 “Ctrl＋X”，同时是一款可以“站起来”的剪刀，基本形式上采用的是传统剪刀的设计，同时加入了一个锥形基底，用来保持剪刀的站立，为了达到平衡，设计师把剪刀把手设计成了圆形，看上去更和谐稳定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135727QpjAD8VcmsHI9efn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76161369\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261357271bgOLGsv6T5uqnJN.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76161369\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135727EN9JwoXQt8b7VqfI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76161369\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135728TurkzLc3HDXFdp6A.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76161369\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}